    OutPutMode
    The DATA_OUTPUT_MODE type is one of: NONE None - action key not injected LINE_FEED Line feed - inject action key in place of ASCII LF (0x0A) character CARRIAGE_RETURN Carriage return - inject action key in place of ASCII CR (0x0D) character TAB_KEY Tab - inject action key in place of a ASCII Tab (0x09) character
